INSERT INTO `coding_article` VALUES (2,'Centos7.2 LNMP环境搭建&配置https服务','<p>文末Tips也许会有你所碰到问题的解决方案</p><p>注意：在搭建环境前应该具备基本的Linux操作常识。其中服务器镜像安装教程略，登录云服务器教程略。</p><p>本教程只适用于Centos7</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">最近租了云服务器后需要在上面搭建环境，但是网上的教程要么不全，要么不适用于centos7。于是记录下自己在成功搭建环境的步骤，一是为大家提供参考，二是给自己留下一些学习笔记。<br/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">一 LNMP搭建</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">这次要搭建的是LNMP，即Linux、Nginx、Php、Mysql。最后会再附上安装PHPmyadmin（Web管理mysql工具）教程。<br/>服务器这边我选择的是腾讯云服务器，镜像是Centos7（其实搭建环境与你选择阿里云、天翼云或者虚拟机都无关，只与镜像版本有关）。如图，镜像安装完成后，服务器已经在运行状态（图一），这边我选择用PuTTY登录云服务器（图二）。</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-b33f1c0df2403994.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1200/format/webp\"/></p><p>图一 腾讯云服务器</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-ad718510a526f0eb.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/702/format/webp\"/></p><p>图二 PuTTY登录云服务器</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">以上为准备工作，下面开始正式安装环境。</p><hr/><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">步骤一 Nginx搭建</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">1.安装ngnix</p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-undefined\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">yum&nbsp;install&nbsp;nginx</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">输入上面的指令后，会出现下图提示。这种类型提示在后面的安装中也会出现，文中无特殊说明一律选择&#39;y&#39; 再回车即可。</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-d3499e3e8b6a6784.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1191/format/webp\"/></p><p>图三 nginx搭建</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">2.启动nginx，并设置为开机启动</p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">systemctl&nbsp;start&nbsp;nginx\r\nsystemctl&nbsp;enable&nbsp;nginx</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">测试：输入上面的指令后，在浏览器中输入服务器 IP能见下图</em><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-3eb06d0f404eddd9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1200/format/webp\"/></p><p>图四 nginx显示</p><p><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">3.配置nginx.conf</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-undefined\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">vim&nbsp;/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">打开文件后，在下图a处新增命令1，b出新增命令b</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-d71411ada05e9845.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/739/format/webp\"/></p><p>图五 nginxconf配置</p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-ruby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">命令1&nbsp;&nbsp;index&nbsp;index.php&nbsp;index.html&nbsp;index.htm;命令2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;location&nbsp;~&nbsp;.php$&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;try_files&nbsp;$uri&nbsp;=404;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;root&nbsp;/usr/share/nginx/html;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fastcgi_pass&nbsp;127.0.0.1:9000;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fastcgi_index&nbsp;index.php;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fastcgi_param&nbsp;SCRIPT_FILENAME&nbsp;$document_root$fastcgi_script_name;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;include&nbsp;fastcgi.conf;}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helv