oll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">tar&nbsp;-xzvf&nbsp;phpMyAdmin-4.0.10.20-all-languages.tar.gz</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">6.将解压后的文件夹改名为phpmyadmin</p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-css\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">mv&nbsp;phpMyAdmin-4.0.10.20-all-languages&nbsp;phpmyadmin</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">测试：在浏览器中输入 IP/phpmyadmin，进入登录页面</em><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-8d7de082b6d54137.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/768/format/webp\"/></p><p>图四 phpmyadmin登录</p><p><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">登录phpmyadmin的用户名和密码是之前设置的登录mysql的密码（默认用户名为root）</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">到这里，phpmyadmin就安装完毕了！</em></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><hr/><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">Tips</h2><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">一.出现下图错误</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">注意：</span>若出现<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">Module &#39;mbstring&#39; already loaded in Unknown on line 0</code>&nbsp;则跳过第2步（如果已经执行了第二步，把那条新增语句删除即可）<br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-8f1e03f79319fd43.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/677/format/webp\"/></p><p>图五 The mbstring extension is missing</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word;\">1.先安装php-mbstring<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">yum install php-mbstring</code><br/>2.编辑php配置文件<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">vim /etc/php.ini</code><br/>在Dynamic Extension下新增语句&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">extension=mbstring.so</code><br/>效果如图<br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-1514e614aee6db9a.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/900/format/webp\"/></p><p>图六 更改phpini</p><br/>3.重启nginx和php-fpm<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">systemctl restart nginx</code><br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">systemctl restart php-fpm</code><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\"><br/></p></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">二.帐号密码正确，登录PHPmyadmin无反应</h3><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">1.更改session的权限<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">chmod -R 777 /var/lib/php/session</code><br/>2.重启nginx和php-fpm<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">systemctl restart nginx</code><br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">systemctl restart php-fpm</code></p></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">三.php连接数据库超时</h3><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">1.在服务器入口规则开放3306端口<br/>2.服务器登录mysql，输入命令<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">grant all PRIVILEGES on 数据库名.* to &#39;用户名&#39;@&#39;主机地址&#39; identified by &#39;登录密码&#39; WITH GRANT OPTION;</code><br/>3.再输入<br/><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border: none; vertical-align: middle; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\">flush privileges;</code></p></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">四.无法正常访问云服务器/服务器不支持ping</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">1.到控制台安全组里面，开启22等一系列端口和ICMP等一系列协议即可</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">2.偶见服务器重启后，暂时ping不可达，静待十几分钟即可</span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">五.phpmyadmin安装后，输入IP/phpmyadmin 显示“404 not found”</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">可能为nginx.conf中php块配置错误，按教程重新配置即可</span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">六.phpmyadmin显示403 forbiddend</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">检查nginx.conf sever块中的index，恢复默认即可</span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">七.phpmyadmin显示“Cannot start session without errors, please check errors given in your PHP and/or webserver log file and configure your PHP installation properly.”</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">在php的配置文件（/etc/php.ini）php.ini中，找到配置项session.auto_start，将其后面的值从0改为1</span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">八.配置https</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">1.去腾讯云免费申请证书<br/>2.根据官方教程在conf中加入一个server（先在安全组中开放443端口）:</p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">server {<br/>listen 443;<br/>server_name www.域名.cn;<br/>ssl on;<br/>ssl_certificate 根目录/1_www.域名.cn_bundle.crt;<br/>ssl_certificate_key 根目录/2_www.域名.cn.key;<br/>ssl_session_timeout 5m;<br/>ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2;<br/>ssl_ciphers ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5:!RC4:!DHE;<br/>ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;<br/>location / {<br/>root 根目录;<br/>index index.html index.htm;<br/>}<br/>}</p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">3.把证书下载到电脑后，在nginx中将1_www.域名.cn_bundle.crt和2_www.域名.cn.key 上传到服务器根目录<br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">特别要注意</span></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">1.conf中括号的配对，以及每条语句后的分号<br/>2.根目录不要写错（如usr写错成user）<br/>4.在所需的server中加入一个跳转语句，这样http会自动跳转到https<br/>rewrite ^(.*) https://$host$ 1 permanent;</p></blockquote><p><br/></p>','20200417/b08b62d8faecd5fefb5a50169c0de73b.jpg',11,0,1,1,1,1587138810,1587138810),(3,'【零基础】使用phpstudy在本地搭建服务器环境','<p>文末Tips也许会有你所碰到问题的解决方案</p><p>请先安装notepad++，双击安装包，之后一直下一步到底即可安装成功。注意在最后一步勾选“Create a shortcut” notepad++下载地址</p><p>注意：后面要打开的文件都用notepad++打开。注意不要用记事本打开，不要用记事本打开，不要用记事本打开 （更新于2020-4-13：实测win10直接用记事本打开，编辑即可）</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-c639ae4288197324.PNG?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/478/format/webp\"/></p><p>图一 右键用notepad++打开</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24px;\">目录</h2><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px;\">一 使用phpstudy搭建本地服务器</h3><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px;\">二 使用mysql-front管理数据库</h3></blockquote><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">一、使用phpstudy搭建本地服务器</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">1.下载phpstudy</span><br/>打开<a href=\"https://links.jianshu.com/go?to=http%3A%2F%2Fphpstudy.php.cn%2F\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(6, 129, 208); text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; outline: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;\">官网</a>，在首页直接点击下载 （或者<a href=\"https://