anshu.io/upload_images/7982212-287350e37e127c27.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/835/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十 测试index</p><p><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">特别注意：如果在按照Tips中的方案更改了端口号。则需要在浏览器中输入127.0.0.1:端口号。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">如：改成了listen 81; 则在浏览器中输入127.0.0.1:81</p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">到这里，你已经把电脑成功搭建成为本地服务器</em></p><hr/><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 22px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">二、使用mysql-front管理数据库</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">注意：在进行以下操作前请先确保服务已经成功启动</em><br/>1.<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">设置mysql密码。打开软件主页面，在服务成功启动后，依次点击 其他选项菜单——mysql工具——重置密码（忘记时）</span><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-1114a4c5592e1513.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/498/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十一 mysql重置密码</p><p><br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">接下来根据提示一步步重置密码即可，请务必记住自己所设置的密码！</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">2.打开软件主页面中的mysql管理器，选择mysql-front<br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-fd4d5d10928e7ec9.PNG?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/491/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十二 mysqlfront管理器</p><p><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">3.点击打开，进入mysql-front主页面</span><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-6471e78740a12fea.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1175/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十三 点击打开</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-fc4797fcc5dca222.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1200/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十四 mysql-front主页面</p><p><br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">注意：可能会直接进入管理主页面，也可能会提示用账号密码登录。用帐号密码登录时，用户名是 root，密码是刚才设置的密码</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">4.鼠标左键选中mysql，即可查看数据库中存在的表。右键mysql可以进行一系列操作，如新建表格等<br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-191b61ee2b16ed1a.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/595/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十五 新建数据库表</p><p><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">5.如图，新建一个名称为a的表。除了名称改成a，其余都不要动。之后点击确定即可。</span><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-cf742d17c2befe83.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/343/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十六 新建表a</p><p><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">6.新建成功后即可在右侧看到表a。双击表a进入详情页即可进行新增字段、编辑已有字段等操作</span><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-8bbf38d24bea69e2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/971/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十七 看到表a了没</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-d6bae2e74d2ff862.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/806/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十八 详情页操作</p><p><br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">到这里，你已经学会了如何管理本地数据库</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><br/></p><hr/><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">Tips</span><br/>1.启动服务时提示80端口被占用<br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">解决方案：</em></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px; background-color: rgb(89, 89, 89); border-left: 6px solid rgb(38, 38, 38); word-break: break-word; line-height: 30px; border-top-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-right-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-bottom-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word;\">1.依次打开 软件安装主目录\\PHPTutorial\\nginx\\conf，用notepad++打开 nginx.conf<br/>2.找到nginx.conf中的sever块，把块中第一句 listen 80; 改成 listen 81; 或者listen 83; 反正不要是80就行。更改后注意保存（ctrl+s）<br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/7982212-48eb8014a5996973.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/757/format/webp\"/></p><p>图十九 改80端口</p><br/>3.返回软件主界面，点击<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">重启</span>。若两个服务都是绿灯且提示服务启动成功则服务已经启动成功了，返回教程第一点中第七步继续往后操作。<br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">注意：若依旧提示端口被占用，打开nginx.conf 把sever中listen 后面的数字再换一个即可</em><br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">特别注意：一但更改nginx.conf，请务必重启服务再进行下一步操作</em><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-word;\"><br/></p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(179, 179, 179); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(61, 61, 61);\">2.nginx跨域问题<br/><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">解决方案：</em><br/>php文件头部添加：</p><p><span class=\"anticon anticon-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; color: inherit; line-height: 0; vertical-align: -0.125em; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span></p><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-bash\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; overflow: scroll auto; overflow-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; overscroll-behavior-x: contain; border-radius: 4px; z-index: 0; padding: 1em 1em 1em 3.8em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; counter-reset: linenumber 0;\">header(&#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin:*&#39;);</pre><p><br/></p>','20200417/97ac4a53d4e9a5f4356a8719eaf46957.jpg',9,1,1,1,1,1587138991,1587138991),(4,'带着你的信仰然后仪式感满满的去学习','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">学习需要信仰。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">自我懂事起就常听到一边强迫我去上各种补习班一边深情看着我的爸妈说：“认真点！你以为让你学这学那是为了谁啊，你是为你自己学习！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">黑色昏暗的高一终于过去，还没来得及等我喘一口大气随之而来却是看起来也不怎么明亮的高二——果然不到两个月我便再一次接受了数学课听不懂双语徘徊在70化学全班最低分每次找排名都从后面开始找的事实。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之后的日子，翻墙出去通宵LOL也变成了家常便饭。每天清晨顶着两个黑眼圈从网吧搭上摩的再揣着从校门口买的两个热乎乎的豆沙包也会赶着去上6：35的晨读——班主任每天必到的那种反正那时候的想法也就是：“学习？学习个屁啊学习！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">时间到了第三次月考出成绩后第二天的第一节晚自习，班主任把我叫到办公室谈心。也不知道为什么一向宁静到极点的办公室那天居然热热闹闹的。“能不能小声点？”老班象征性的喊了一嗓子，但似乎并没有卵用。于是老班领着我走到办公室门口一棵树下的长凳上很耐心的开始帮我分析每一门学科，告诉我该怎么学、怎么做...也许是被什么触动了，也或许是一直跟着老班的思维思考比较累，那天下晚自习后，我取消了当天的通宵计划。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一睡到觉到6点10分，当时精力那叫一个充沛啊，久旱逢甘霖一般让我感觉我能打五个。出门，走到教室，坐下。教室里早就回响着各种背单词，读文言文，甚至读生物知识点的声音。“单词发音不准，生物成绩还过得去”我心里这样想着然后打开了那本《高考必备古文》。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“夫光阴者百代之过客也！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“噫吁嚱！蜀道之难难于上青天！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“寻寻觅觅冷冷清清凄凄惨惨戚戚！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“天道...酬勤！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就像被闪电劈了一下，我一个冷颤顿时头皮发麻到脚底板。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我抬起头深吸了一口气然后慢慢呼出，紧接着又左右扫视了一下：教室还是几秒前的那个教室，各种读书声依旧充斥在耳边。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">天道？什么是天道？酬勤？我该怎么勤她该怎么酬？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我思索了一会儿，随后第一次自己为自己量身定制了一个学习计划——一个长期的学习计划，一个直到高考后才废止的计划。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">期末考试——双语70+，高二下学期双语70+，高三上学期双语90+，高考双语100+。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根生万里，一夜枝繁叶茂。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">时隔今日，我看着“酬勤”两个字依旧是闪闪发光，刺眼无比。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">学习需要仪式感。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经常能听到亲友们抱怨什么，过年没年味儿啦，过节没有以前有意思啦诸类。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那你过年接红包的时候有想过为什么这一天非得收红包？贴对联的时候呢？吃饺子的时候呢？吃月饼的时候呢？吃粽子的时候呢？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为在你看来这是一种形式，而实际上这是一种仪式。一旦仪式被去掉就总会少点儿意思。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">形式，华而不实。在某种情况下甚至会被省略；仪式，朴实无华。不会被省略而且是你后续行为的必须准备。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同学：“啊好无聊啊整天没事儿做。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“没事做你去学习啊！”我看着他说。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“在寝室学着没意思！”他无奈的笑着说。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后看着他继续呆在寝室无聊着。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以我一般都不会在寝室学习，该要学习的时候我就会下楼出门右转去图书馆。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为在我看来去图书馆的那段路上隔着“过年过节一顿饭完事儿”和“大吉大利今晚吃鸡”。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而能把“信仰”和“仪式感”完美融合的人，在我看来应该算是神人一般的存在了。而这时，我的两个观点就会升华成：**学习是一种信仰。**</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">显然我还做不到。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">暂时。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">——2017.9.17于图书馆</p>','20200418/b5adaba1a97dc85f90fd7f134ad9c278.jpg',4,0,1,2,1,1587139256,1587139256),(5,'不安的乐观','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就在刚刚，我去阅览室翻开了一本《2017年计算机考研基础》指导书。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我是怀着渴望的心情翻开这本书的，而把书放回去后我内心却十分忐忑并充满着不安、</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我从来都没有这么不安过，从来没有过。心脏在颤抖着，不是跳动而是颤抖，包括我写这句话的时候。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我在暑假正式决定考研，而且决心要考一个好学校，这是我这么多年来作出的，为数不多的重大决定之一。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在此之前的高考也算是我人生的一个重大决定，可为什么就没有今天这种不安感呢？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高考，一群人，老师、家长、小伙伴。方向明确，力求高分。不仅是自己的决定也是人生的必然阶段而且决定后都不会半途而废，残酷但不惨酷。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">考研，一个人，一台电脑，一笔一纸。方向模糊，步骤繁琐。是自己单独做出的决定而且居然是可以半途而废的，残酷也很惨酷。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">没有小伙伴没有排名榜没有苦口婆心的教导甚至都没有充足的准备？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">放弃吗？那坚持？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">坚持对我来说是一种奢求。我这么多年所一直坚持着的也就是吃饭和睡觉了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以至于前段时间为了安慰自己，我在锻炼身体这件事上还故意混淆了“坚持”和“保持”。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每天锻炼是保持，一月一次是保持，一年一次也是保持。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我真他娘的是个天才。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;——2017.9.19/17：25 于图书馆</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">天生是个乐天主义者——反馈到我身上也就是心态能很快的自我调节（就像坐垂直过山车一样刺激）。前后不过半小时我发现我又能冷静分析问题啦，老子又能皮啦！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“言必行，行必果。既然决定了考研那你就去啊去实现你的梦想啊少年！”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那我就当一回小人又何妨？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">考研难啊难啊是真的难，外校双非考研简直就是徒手爬珠峰？我邓某人很少会碰到这种难题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">孤独？你不够优秀是因为你不够孤独！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">没小伙伴？不还还有对手吗？一生之敌不就是一生所爱？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">摸黑？前路漫漫要是绝对黑暗难道找到一个小亮点很难吗？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">坚持不了？我今天就把“坚持”和“保持”划开界限！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">数学不行？我看十遍行不行？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英语不行？我刷提刷到蓝屏行不行？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有什么，数据结构、编译原理、操作系统、计算机网络尽管过来啊！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你们顶多让我跪下躺下，认输？不存在的！</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那就狂一年行不行？疯一年好不好？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(50, 58, 69); text-indent: 28px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ——2017.9.19/17：51